    rdfs:label "Regulatory Report"@en ;
    rdfs:label "监管报告"@zh ;
    rdfs:comment "Compliance reports submitted periodically to regulators, e.g., capital adequacy, AML reports"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "金融机构按监管要求定期提交的合规报告，如资本充足率报告、反洗钱报告等"@zh .

